Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.65,0:22:27.90,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur2\fad(500,500)}Sappy old remedies 無法確定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:31.07,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur2\fad(500,500)}即使如此 go up the river
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.07,0:22:34.24,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur2\fad(500,500)}咬緊牙關 became a ladder
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:37.33,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur2\fad(500,500)}連有眼涙都宛如燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.33,0:22:41.08,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur2\fad(500,500)}一個sign 一個light
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.08,0:22:47.13,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur2\fad(500,500)}但願沒有黎明的夜晚 歌聲不會間斷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.13,0:22:52.72,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur2\fad(500,500)}但願不要困在和彷徨迷惑的夢境裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:22:58.89,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}但願交錯的足跡們不再執著過去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:05.32,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}但願就算你一旦失足 也千萬別放手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:11.16,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}I'm the prover I am the prover
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.16,0:23:17.66,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}但願能勇敢面對沒有結束的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.66,0:23:23.50,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}I'm the prover 生命的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.50,0:23:30.13,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}還在發出聲響 與你一起
